### ======================================================
### ASSINATURA DA PLATAFORMA — Mercado Pago (fluxo de teste)
### ======================================================
### Pré-requisitos (.env):
### - PLATFORM_SUBSCRIPTION_PROVIDER=mercadopago (ou omita; padrão é mercadopago)
### - MERCADOPAGO_ACCESS_TOKEN = token de TESTE da conta da aplicação (painel MP)
### - BACKEND_URL = URL pública da API (ex.: https://xxx.ngrok-free.app) se quiser webhooks reais do MP
### - FRONTEND_URL
### Webhook assinatura: POST {BACKEND_URL}/webhooks/mercadopago/subscription
###   Em desenvolvimento, sem MERCADOPAGO_WEBHOOK_SECRET_KEY o backend aceita corpo sem x-signature.
###   Com a chave definida, calcule HMAC-SHA256(hex) do corpo RAW em x-signature.
###
### ATENÇÃO: cada combinação paymentMethod + rota MP é exclusiva:
### - PIX ou BOLETO no /start  →  só POST .../mercadopago/transparent-payment
### - CARD no /start           →  só preapproval + preapproval/card (+ token MP.js na etapa 2)
### Chamar preapproval com checkout criado como PIX → 400 SubscriptionCheckoutPreapprovalNotCardError
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@subscriberEmail = jhowgama21@gmail.com
@subscriberPassword = senha123
### Um slug por tentativa de checkout (409 = subdomínio já usado):
@subdomainPix = rock-valley-studio
@subdomainCard = meu-studio-card-001
@checkoutId = 74ac7d17-7d82-4e5e-8f3a-51dc54c001cc
@subscriberToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyOWQ4NzMxMS0xYjY0LTRiMmUtYjMzYy03MDI1NzhiMDMyOGMiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU0Mzk4NDUsImV4cCI6MTc3NjA0NDY0NX0.AnFLSAOg7STckSTn19PxtY-c915KlbPycGQ82bbfWTc
@ownerToken = COLE_JWT_OWNER_PARA_APPROVE_MANUAL

### ------------------------------------------------------
### 0) Login do assinante (USER que vai contratar o plano)
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{subscriberEmail}}",
  "password": "{{subscriberPassword}}"
}

### ########################################################
### FLUXO A — PIX (ou BOLETO): transparent-payment apenas
### ########################################################

### A1) Iniciar checkout com paymentMethod PIX (ou BOLETO)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/start
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planTier": "STARTER",
  "billingCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "studioName": "Studio Teste MP",
  "domainType": "SUBDOMAIN",
  "subdomain": "{{subdomainPix}}",
  "paymentMethod": "PIX",
  "totalAmount": 5
}

### A2) Conferir checkout
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### A3) Criar pagamento PIX/boleto no MP
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/mercadopago/transparent-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payerIdentificationType": "CPF",
  "payerIdentificationNumber": "12345678909"
}

### ########################################################
### FLUXO B — CARTÃO: preapproval (não use o mesmo checkout do fluxo A)
### ########################################################

## B1) NOVO checkout obrigatório com paymentMethod CARD
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/start
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planTier": "STARTER",
  "billingCycle": "MONTHLY",
  "studioName": "Studio Teste MP Card",
  "domainType": "SUBDOMAIN",
  "subdomain": "{{subdomainCard}}",
  "paymentMethod": "CARD",
  "totalAmount": 5
}

### B2) Etapa 1 — preapproval pendente (só com checkoutId do B1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/8f9776c8-3943-4631-b1e6-56b7ca3c8ae1/mercadopago/preapproval
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### B3) Etapa 2 — token MercadoPago.js
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/8f9776c8-3943-4631-b1e6-56b7ca3c8ae1/mercadopago/preapproval/card
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cardTokenId": "TOKEN_RETORNADO_PELO_MP.JS"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### Webhook (simulado em local) — pagamento approved no MP
### Use paymentId real do fluxo A (transparent) após pagar no sandbox.
### Com túnel + webhook no painel MP, não precisa disparar manualmente.
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/mercadopago/subscription
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment",
  "data": { "id": "SUBSTITUA_PELO_PAYMENT_ID_DO_MP" }
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### Aprovar manual (OWNER) — fallback sem webhook
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentReference": "teste-manual-mp-1"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### Conferir status final do checkout
### ------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription-checkout/{{checkoutId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}
